You can find these new arrivals on their site tonight at midnight pst & use my code KRISTA25 to save yourself 25% off your entire purchase all day Sunday! #vicipartner Who wants a $200 gift card?! Like + comment on this pic and I’ll send it to 10 of ya! #hortwin

node.text: Happy 6th Birthday to our Kolly girl! 👸🏼 she’s the definition of original, she’s lipstick’s #1 fan since day 1, she never lets us go a day without busting up laughing, and this year she became the world’s best big sis! She’s sassy, she’s stylish, she’s sweet, and now she’s freaking SIX! 🥺 love you Kolly girl! #happybirthday #kollygirl

node.text: What happens in Vegas STAYS in Vegas…like this front tuck BRUCE. Stop trying to make the front tuck happen, it’s not going to happen! 🤪 also, please swipe for Kamp’s golfing debut🏌️‍♂️🥺 This dress I’m wearing is actually a romper which is the best thing to ever happen, riiiight?! (AND it has pockets 🙌🏻). @vicidolls new arrivals will be on their website at midnight pst! You can use code KRISTA25 all day Sunday! Like + tag a friend so that you both can win a $100 gift card! I’ll pick 10 of you from the comments and 10 of you from stories! #vicipartner #vegasbaby
